reviewText: Just as expected. Haven't watched all the titles but so far, so good.

When I bought this a year or so ago I was excited but didn't watch any of the movies until just now. I tried to watch Panic Room but there were no captions or options for subtitles.
Id like my money back.
Great price for relatively good movies.
Exciting collection of thrillers that will get your heart racing.
I did not like it...The language was to abusive for the children and myself...No subtitles...
In my opinion, Panic Room is the only  movie in this collection worth watching. All of them, however, are laced with unnecessary profanity.

At this price, you can't even buy one of these movies right now. All came as 2 discs in one case. Great quality and movies are all very good. I mostly bought because of Panic Room, but Perfect Stranger was good too! Those are the only 2 I've watched so far.
